Job Purpose
Perform adopting new technologies to implant into, to fuse into or to replace with existing systems for gaining leaps in performance, benefits and capabilities of the users.

Key Accountabilities
i. To evaluate, to study, to analyze feasibility of adopting new technologies including but not limited to architecting, methodologies, systems, tools;
ii. To confirm and to assess gaps, risks, occasion, use stories, as details as possible by consulting external/internal subject matter experts, or by seeking for supports from other teams as well;
iii. To find out suitable approach on adopting new technologies, to plan, to prove, to estimate the migration of adopting new technologies on the existing systems; 
iv. To compile well organized documentation, to deliver introduction, training, guiding, presenting results of proof, plan, context of adopting new technologies;
v. To collaborate with teams to conduct the migration of adopting new technology on the existing systems;
vi. To work with vendors to solve problems from or to get support for using software/hardware solutions provided by vendors;
vii. To provide supports to other teams on adopting new technologies to generate synergy.

